---
// The Archipelago Learning System component
---

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">The Archipelago Learning System</h2>
    <div class="content-text">
      <p>Dao-Yu-101 organizes knowledge like an island world.</p>
      <p>Each subject becomes an archipelago.</p>
      <p>Inside each archipelago are islands representing learning topics.</p>
      <p>Every island contains lessons and activities that help students understand the topic step by step.</p>
      
      <div class="structure-explanation">
        <h3>Simple structure explanation:</h3>
        <div class="structure-list">
          <div class="structure-item">Subject → Archipelago</div>
          <div class="structure-item">Topic → Island</div>
          <div class="structure-item">Lesson → Activities on the island</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .content-section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,250,252,0.95), rgba(241,245,249,0.85));
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: #1f2937;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .content-text {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .content-text p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .structure-explanation {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 30px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.3);
  }

  .structure-explanation h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #111827;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .structure-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .structure-item {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #059669;
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
    padding: 15px 25px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #059669;
    text-align: left;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .structure-explanation {
      padding: 20px 15px;
    }

    .structure-item {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 12px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>